{"id":18362,"date":"2019-06-12T18:40:31","date_gmt":"2019-06-12T11:40:31","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=18362"},"modified":"2019-11-16T15:08:17","modified_gmt":"2019-11-16T08:08:17","slug":"tao-email-theo-ten-mien","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/usecase\/tao-email-theo-ten-mien","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi ImprovMX v\u00e0 Gmail"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\"><strong>V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n n\u00e0y<\/strong> b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t Gmail c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n DUY NH\u1ea4T nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n cho nhi\u1ec1u website kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed nh\u01b0 G-Suite hay Office365 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u00f3a v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, hay t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c email hosting mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed nh\u01b0 Yandex hay Zoho Mail.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed th\u00ec t\u1ed1t r\u1ed3i, c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t nhanh, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng k\u00e8m theo chi ph\u00ed h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd khi b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi n\u00ean b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed thay th\u1ebf. C\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u01a1n v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00e1 \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00ec n\u00f3 khi kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u h\u1ebft.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng trong qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd. EMAIL FORWARDING l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n. Ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Gmail c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u1ed1i \u0111a 10 email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"hint\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi blogger, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00f3m, \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u blog v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u00f9ng l\u00fac. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u00f3m ri\u00eang th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 h\u00e3y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng G Suite tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n, Email Forwarding v\u00e0 Email Alias l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"665\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/domain-email-1024x665.png\" alt=\"Domain Email\" class=\"wp-image-18447\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/domain-email-1024x665.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/domain-email-218x142.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/domain-email-300x195.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/domain-email-700x455.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/domain-email-768x499.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/domain-email.png 1172w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi, email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n hay c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 email domain ho\u1eb7c email doanh nghi\u1ec7p. C\u00e1c email n\u00e0y c\u00f3 d\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0&nbsp;<em>cuong@cuongthach.com<\/em> ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0&nbsp;<em>cuong@gmail.com<\/em>. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Email forwarding<\/strong>&#8230;? L\u00e0 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp email t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp tin nh\u1eafn hay cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. Khuy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a email forwarding l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u01b0u tr\u1eef c\u00e1c email g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn, m\u00e0 email c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ebd (email \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp) s\u1ebd l\u01b0u tr\u1eef nh\u1eefng email n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Email Alias<\/strong> hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 email nick-name. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nick-name b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean Facebook, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00ean th\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Email Alias c\u0169ng v\u1eady, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i email g\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>V\u00ed d\u1ee5:&nbsp;<em>cuong@gmail.com<\/em>&nbsp;l\u00e0 email g\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, 2 email&nbsp;<em>cuong@cuongthach.com<\/em>&nbsp;v\u00e0&nbsp;<em>support@cuongthach.com<\/em>&nbsp;s\u1ebd l\u00e0 2 email alias c\u1ee7a&nbsp;<em>cuong@gmail.com<\/em>. Khi t\u00f4i g\u1eedi email t\u1eeb&nbsp;<em>cuong@cuongthach.com<\/em>&nbsp;th\u00ec th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0&nbsp;<strong>email \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so\u1ea1n v\u00e0 g\u1eedi tr\u00ean email g\u1ed1c&nbsp;cuong@gmail.com<\/strong>.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1c kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m tr\u00ean gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m quen tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00e0m theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>ImprovMX l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/improvmx-slogan-1024x576.png\" alt=\"Improvmx Slogan\" class=\"wp-image-18444\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/improvmx-slogan-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/improvmx-slogan-218x123.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/improvmx-slogan-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/improvmx-slogan-700x394.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/improvmx-slogan-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/improvmx-slogan.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/improvmx.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">ImprovMX<\/a>&nbsp;l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 online mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed (c\u00f3 g\u00f3i tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed cao c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n) gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n sang email c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (Gmail) \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n ImprovMX mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o 10 t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n kh\u00e1c nhau, v\u00e0 m\u1ed7i t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n cho ph\u00e9p chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp 10 email alias kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n ImprovMX tr\u01b0\u1edbc, sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a ImprovMX \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a ImprovMX kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n v\u00e0 email c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>ImprovMX s\u1ebd g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t Magic Link (Link \u0111\u0103c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n m\u1eadt kh\u1ea9u v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ghi nh\u1edb cho l\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp sau \u1edf c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb). B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n click v\u00e0o link l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o giao di\u1ec7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Thi\u1ebfp l\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn email \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &#8211; Chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp email (Email forwarding)<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/email-forwarding-1024x600.png\" alt=\"Email Forwarding\" class=\"wp-image-18449\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/email-forwarding.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/email-forwarding-218x128.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/email-forwarding-300x176.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/email-forwarding-700x410.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/email-forwarding-768x450.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp m\u1ecdi email g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n sang h\u1ed9p th\u01b0 email c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ImprovMX.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Th\u00eam 2 MX records c\u1ee7a ImprovMX v\u00e0o domain DNS<\/strong>. C\u00e1ch th\u00eam kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi domain DNS. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a quen h\u00e3y xem b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"\/client\/knowledge-base\/module\/xac-thuc-domain-mailchimp\/\" target=\"_blank\">H\u01af\u1edaNG D\u1eaaN X\u00c1C TH\u1ef0C DOMAIN KHI D\u00d9NG MAILCHIMP<\/a>&nbsp;&#8211;&nbsp;<strong>C\u00e1ch 2<\/strong> ho\u1eb7c tham kh\u1ea3o nhanh&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/improvmx.com\/guides\/provider\/cloudflare\" target=\"_blank\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn th\u00eam MX record c\u1ee7a ImprovMX v\u1edbi Cloudflare t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/a>.<\/li><li><strong>T\u1ea1o email alias<\/strong>. Sau khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u00eam 2 MX record. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o t\u1ed1i \u0111a 10 email alias cho t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110i\u1ec1n v\u00e0o \u00f4&nbsp;<strong>new-alias<\/strong>. M\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh email c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd l\u00e0 email b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd ImprovMX, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y \u00fd n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n.<\/li><li><strong>Ki\u1ec3m tra<\/strong>. B\u1ea1n ki\u1ec3m tra b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t email kh\u00e1c (kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng email c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd ImprovMX) so\u1ea1n tin \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra th\u1eed \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn tin hay ch\u01b0a. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn th\u00ec ch\u00fac m\u1eebng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng!<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p class=\"hint\">M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u01b0u \u00fd c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 h\u00e3y x\u00f3a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 MX Records trong Domain DNS n\u1ebfu c\u00f3. Ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 2 MX record c\u1ee7a ImprovMX m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: Thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi email \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &#8211; D\u00f9ng SMTP c\u1ee7a Gmail<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/SMTP-de-gui-email-1024x600.png\" alt=\"Smtp De Gui Email\" class=\"wp-image-18452\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/SMTP-de-gui-email.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/SMTP-de-gui-email-218x128.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/SMTP-de-gui-email-300x176.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/SMTP-de-gui-email-700x410.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/SMTP-de-gui-email-768x450.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh b\u01b0\u1edbc 1, b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn email m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi email \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t SMTP \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi email \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng SMTP mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a Gmail \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n g\u1eedi email (B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c SMTP mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Mailgun \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n, tuy nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i th\u00edch d\u00f9ng SMTP c\u1ee7a Gmail h\u01a1n v\u00ec Mailgun \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh cho Email Marketing th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"ImprovMX c\u00f3 b\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n g\u1eedi email t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y ( English). (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/improvmx.com\/guides\/send-emails-using-gmail\" target=\"_blank\">ImprovMX c\u00f3 b\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n g\u1eedi email t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y ( English).<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a hi\u1ec3u h\u00e3y xem h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>B\u1ea1n PH\u1ea2I b\u1eadt b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt 2 l\u1edbp 2FA c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Gmail.&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/landing\/2step\/\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1eadt b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt 2FA cho Gmail t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/a>.<\/li><li>T\u1ea1o Gmail App Password. <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"V\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/security.google.com\/settings\/security\/apppasswords\" target=\"_blank\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o App Password<\/a>. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i copy m\u1eadt kh\u1ea9u l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u01b0\u1edbc 5.<\/li><li>Th\u00eam email alias v\u00e0o Gmail. V\u00e0o <strong>Gmail<\/strong> &gt; <strong>Setting <\/strong>&gt; <strong>Accounts and Import<\/strong> &gt; <strong>Send email as:<\/strong> &gt; <strong>add another email address<\/strong>. <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Link nhanh (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/mail.google.com\/mail\/u\/0\/#settings\/accounts\" target=\"_blank\">Link nhanh<\/a>.<\/li><li>\u0110i\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tin ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eedi bao g\u1ed3m T\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eedi v\u00e0 Email ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eedi. V\u1edbi Email ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eedi b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n. Nh\u1edb b\u1ecf ch\u1ecdn &#8220;treat as an alias&#8221;.<\/li><li>\u0110i\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tin Email. SMTP l\u00e0 &#8220;smtp.gmail.com&#8221;, Username l\u00e0 Email c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n (Gmail g\u1ed1c), Password l\u00e0 m\u1eadt kh\u1ea9u b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u1edf b\u01b0\u1edbc 2, Port: 587, TLS gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean.<\/li><li>X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t email t\u1eeb Gmail \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn xem b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 hay kh\u00f4ng. H\u00e3y l\u00e0m theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn trong email \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn (\u0111i\u1ec1n code l\u00e0 xong).<\/li><li>Ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi email b\u1eb1ng email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh r\u1ed3i. Khi b\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi email hay so\u1ea1n th\u01b0 m\u1edbi h\u00e3y b\u1ea5m v\u00e0o \u00f4 From \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eedi. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y Email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh g\u1eedi email nh\u01b0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/app-password-google.gif\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"625\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/app-password-google.gif\" alt=\"App Password Google\" class=\"wp-image-18455\"\/><\/a><figcaption>App Password<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/smtp-sender-info-gmail-1.gif\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"625\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/smtp-sender-info-gmail-1.gif\" alt=\"Smtp Sender Info Gmail 1\" class=\"wp-image-18456\"\/><\/a><figcaption>\u0110i\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tin ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eedi v\u00e0 email g\u1eedi (Email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n Alias)<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/smtp-gmail.gif\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"625\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/smtp-gmail.gif\" alt=\"Smtp Gmail\" class=\"wp-image-18457\"\/><\/a><figcaption>C\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh SMTP Server theo Gmail (Ch\u00fa \u00fd: Email Gmail c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n + App Password \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o)<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eb9o hay khi b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n &#8211; Gmail tips<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">M\u1eb9o #1: C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng email alias tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi email.<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh s\u1ef1 nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh reply email b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 email c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (Gmail) thay v\u00ec d\u00f9ng email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u1ede giao di\u1ec7n Gmail, b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o <strong>Setting<\/strong> &gt; <strong>Accounts and Important<\/strong> &gt; Ch\u1ecdn <strong>Reply from the same address the message sent to<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Cai-dat-tu-dong-dung-dia-chi-email-tra-loi.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"997\" height=\"569\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Cai-dat-tu-dong-dung-dia-chi-email-tra-loi.png\" alt=\"Cai Dat Tu Dong Dung Dia Chi Email Tra Loi\" class=\"wp-image-18436\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Cai-dat-tu-dong-dung-dia-chi-email-tra-loi.png 997w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Cai-dat-tu-dong-dung-dia-chi-email-tra-loi-218x124.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Cai-dat-tu-dong-dung-dia-chi-email-tra-loi-300x171.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Cai-dat-tu-dong-dung-dia-chi-email-tra-loi-700x399.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Cai-dat-tu-dong-dung-dia-chi-email-tra-loi-768x438.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 997px) 100vw, 997px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng Reply from the same address the message was sent s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n tr\u00e1nh nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn v\u1edbi t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n email c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n khi REPLY ai \u0111\u00f3<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">M\u1eb9o #2: D\u00e1n nh\u00e3n ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t email \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n n\u00e0o<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd d\u00e1n nh\u00e3n label cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 email n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. M\u1eb9o n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 th\u1ea5y email n\u00e0o l\u00e0 email g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, email n\u00e0o l\u00e0 email g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t quy t\u1eafc l\u1ecdc email theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Tao-filter-trong-Gmail.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"521\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Tao-filter-trong-Gmail-1024x521.png\" alt=\"Tao Filter Trong Gmail\" class=\"wp-image-18437\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Tao-filter-trong-Gmail-1024x521.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Tao-filter-trong-Gmail-218x111.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Tao-filter-trong-Gmail-300x153.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Tao-filter-trong-Gmail-700x356.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Tao-filter-trong-Gmail-768x391.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Tao-filter-trong-Gmail.png 1249w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>T\u1ea1o Filter m\u1edbi trong Gmail Setting<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/cai-dat-quy-tac-cho-Filter.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"790\" height=\"395\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/cai-dat-quy-tac-cho-Filter.png\" alt=\"Cai Dat Quy Tac Cho Filter\" class=\"wp-image-18438\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/cai-dat-quy-tac-cho-Filter.png 790w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/cai-dat-quy-tac-cho-Filter-218x109.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/cai-dat-quy-tac-cho-Filter-300x150.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/cai-dat-quy-tac-cho-Filter-700x350.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/cai-dat-quy-tac-cho-Filter-768x384.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 790px) 100vw, 790px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t quy t\u1eafc cho Filter: b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 email n\u00e0o g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn email t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn nh\u00e3n<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/chon-new-label-trong-Gmail.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"967\" height=\"594\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/chon-new-label-trong-Gmail.png\" alt=\"Chon New Label Trong Gmail\" class=\"wp-image-18439\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/chon-new-label-trong-Gmail.png 967w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/chon-new-label-trong-Gmail-218x134.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/chon-new-label-trong-Gmail-300x184.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/chon-new-label-trong-Gmail-700x430.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/chon-new-label-trong-Gmail-768x472.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 967px) 100vw, 967px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Apply the label: Ch\u1ecdn New Label &gt; \u0110\u1eb7t t\u00ean cho nh\u00e3n. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean b\u1eb1ng domain lu\u00f4n nh\u01b0 domain.com<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/tao-filter.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"787\" height=\"597\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/tao-filter.png\" alt=\"Tao Filter\" class=\"wp-image-18441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/tao-filter.png 787w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/tao-filter-218x165.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/tao-filter-300x228.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/tao-filter-700x531.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/tao-filter-768x583.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 787px) 100vw, 787px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Stick ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00f4 nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean v\u00e0 b\u1ea5m n\u00fat t\u1ea1o Filter &#8211; &#8220;Create filter&#8221;<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u00e3n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o xong, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4 m\u00e0u cho nh\u00e3n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngay email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c trong h\u1ed9p th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/label-color.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"370\" height=\"288\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/label-color.jpg\" alt=\"Label Color\" class=\"wp-image-18442\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/label-color.jpg 370w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/label-color-218x170.jpg 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/label-color-300x234.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u00e1ch th\u00eam m\u00e0u cho nh\u00e3n v\u1edbi m\u00e0u c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Gmail c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Gmail c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 <strong>15 GB<\/strong> l\u01b0u tr\u1eef t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng<\/li><li>Google s\u1ebd d\u00e1n nh\u00e3n &#8220;<em>via Gmail.com<\/em>&#8221; trong email ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ea1i sao n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m nh\u1ecf th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp quy\u1ec1n h\u1ea1n cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 email th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong nh\u00f3m. Ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c x\u00f3a v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin c\u00f4ng ty. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u01b0u tr\u1eef email (t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 email \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0u tr\u1eef trong m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n email c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n duy nh\u1ea5t). Khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ngh\u1ec9 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd k\u00e9o theo to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 email v\u00e0 b\u00ed m\u1eadt kinh doanh c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y ho\u1eb7c xem l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e1c email.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u00f3i chung r\u1ea5t r\u1ee7i ro v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf cho c\u00f4ng ty \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, n\u00ean d\u00f9ng G Suite s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n cho c\u00f4ng ty, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 blogger th\u00ec c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b<em>\u1ea1n c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn, h\u00e3y chia s\u1ebb \u1edf ph\u1ea7n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e9 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n!<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1ea1o email theo t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng giao ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecdc gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t email marketing trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":18389,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"close","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[198],"tags":[194],"featured_image_urls":{"full":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/email-theo-ten-mien.png",1024,512,false],"thumbnail":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/email-theo-ten-mien-300x150.png",270,135,true],"medium":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2